name    'tobw-hadoop'
version '0.0.1'
author 'Tobias Wiens'
dependency 'viirya/java', '0.0.1'
summary 'Install Hadoop MapReduce Version 2.3.0 and provides its java dependency with the jdk1.7.0_51. Then installs stratosphere on top of yarn.'
description "This module deploys Hadoop with yarn and hdfs. All ssh-ing is replace through puppet commands. So that the instalation process can be fully automated. Additionally it starts a script which automatically configures the hadoop cluster through the instances which register at the puppet master."
project_page 'https://github.com/tobwiens/puppet-hadoop-nossh-stratosphere'
license 'The MIT License'
